PrecisTransfer to the Province of New Brunswick of the administration and control over the Canadian section of five international highway bridges connecting the Province to the State of Maine, U.S.A., at the following locations: (1) St. Stephen - Calais; (2) St. Leonard - Van Buren; (3) St. Croix - Vanceboro; (4) Edmundston - Madawaska; and (5) Clair - Fort Kent.
